{"tid":150994,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"用1.2倍速睇左兇手還未睡之觀眾已熟睡","createTime":"2017-03-10T13:24:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T14:53:18.000Z","uid":6436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"127036b3a473af4e8e05e03c8db92320b47b74d7","tid":150994,"uid":6436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T13:24:39.000Z","msg":"未睇之前已經知道係爛片黎，聽講用垃圾黎形容都侮辱左垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係睇完之後覺得未至於超級爛片既，只係懸疑片黎講佢真係好失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一味靠大聲呢啲低裝手法嚇鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條橋扭完又扭扭完又扭，但係完全意料之內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋dklm冇邏輯可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再講個cast，jm都算啦起碼睇得下，但係你老味用杜德偉做男主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 演技垃圾仲要扮高智商罪犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩有林家棟救返少少，做賤男入型入格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想俾佢摑鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw用1.2倍速（或者更快）睇爛片唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算浪費生命都叫做對得住自己<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/10/212424_e5df5209e894c340ea1fd22e5c7ad7f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F10%2F212424_e5df5209e894c340ea1fd22e5c7ad7f7.jpg&h=03cf2bab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c860847987ae2f595af657749c26a6adbb8133d","tid":150994,"uid":11851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:25:54.000Z","msg":"垃圾到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n浪費時間，浪費錢，拍到咁都唔知為咩"},{"pid":"2e0b41a28b573beb72edfed0b969137b4fee9e9e","tid":150994,"uid":7030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T14:34:30.000Z","msg":"邊度有得睇？<img src=\"/assets/face